    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-80d2-bd80-fa87abbf9bfa",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Work uses EEG to record physiological information from learners to predict SRL traits during online learning. The authors also propose a form of providing feedback to train online learner brains to improve their SRL skills. ",
